==Description==
[...logging in...]

''riddle'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 02:16<br />''■ It's Hanami's birthday stream today, but why does it feel like we just celebrated it last month?''

''I'm on Fire!'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 02:18<br />''■ She claims her birthday is on August 73rd... Try finding THAT on a calendar!''

''Voice of 873'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 02:20<br />''■ Hanami updated her status: "Wow! So many gifts! Thank you everyone! Also, if possible, please help clear out Hanami's wishlist~ Love ya ♥"''

''riddle'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 02:21<br />''■ I know she's trying to drain my wallet dry! But you know what? I'm totally cool with it~ My dear Hanami~ My precious Hanami~''

[Replying to riddle] ''KappaKami'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 02:26<br />''■ You're that person who was just online, aren't you? All those gifts you're sending, you're just trying to make yourself into a top fan, right? Our Hanami already has her own fanbase, so stop trying to force your way in.''<br />''■ You think I can't look up your ID? You're a lawless thug, a criminal. You think I don't know that?''<br />''■ You're pretending to be a Hanami fan like us, but you're really just trying to build up a fanbase to cash in on her popularity and trending status. Get out of the stream!''

[Replying to KappaKami] ''riddle'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 02:41<br />''■ Who are you to talk? What's it to you? At least I showed up for the livestream. What have YOU been doing?''

''I'm on Fire!'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 02:45<br />''■ ...Are there only Hanami stans in this forum? No haters around? If you're a fan, head straight to the livestream channel!''

[Replying to I'm on Fire!] ''\(^o^)/~'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 03:00<br />''■ I'm a hardcore anti-fan!''<br />''■ We need to make a plan to really mess with her and her fans. Not just get her canceled, but get her arrested!''<br />''■ I've DMed you the group chat link ♥''

[Replying to \(^o^)/~] ''I'm on Fire!'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 03:02<br />''■ I've joined several anti-fan groups. We act like bros normally, but the moment something happens, they bicker internally. Heh, I'm done with this.''

''Voice of 873'' posted on Aug 7 (Fri) 03:03<br />''■ Hanami updated her status: "Nami-nami, nighty-niiiight"''

[...logging off.]

As the night draws to an end, digital nomads in cyberspace peer around curiously, exchanging fragmented discussions and offering ambiguous stances. Ultimately, none will be remembered...

Virtual characters celebrate virtual birthdays, as virtual chaos seeps into chaotic reality.

